{
  "stem": "2996.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one of the people belonging to that federation or association didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said to themselves, since Nazis don't like Jews, we should do it to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, your enemies, my friends, my friends, your enemies and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They looked for a Jewish lawyer to help them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And since they found under attorneys, a man by the name of Louis Greenbaum, or Greenbaum.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They went to him with their problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this guy then went to that little Jewish group that I described.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they were concerned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They handled that case, and the Nazis were defeated in this thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So all of this was the beginning of what later became the thing that I worked for full time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now you wanted me to say something else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And now I've deserted you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I forgot it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, they simply fought whichever way they-- incidentally, one more thing-- I should back up a little bit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, the carried classified ads listing open jobs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the last line, not always but frequently, was 'whites and gentiles only.' So this little group was concerned with that and negotiated for quite some time with the bosses in order to get them to refuse to accept ads like that.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They did all of this before I appeared on the scene.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now I came on the scene in order to do that story, getting some material out of the German-- the sons of that aristocrat.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, once I got there, I met with one of the people who belonged to that little group.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody took me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is the guy who phoned from Chicago.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we met.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this fellow was connected with the motion picture industry.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
